OL,6,FRetired GP John Macdonald, from
OL,7,FWigtown, has prostate cancer. He is
OL,8,Fnot terminally ill, but supports the
OL,9,Fprinciple of assisted dying.
OL,11,FHe said: "I think people should have
OL,12,Fautonomy over how and where and when
OL,13,Fthey wish to die just as they have
OL,14,Fautonomy over every other aspect of
OL,15,Ftheir lives.
