OL,6,F"I've had a cancer diagnosis myself,
OL,7,Fand ultimately, in the future, if I
OL,8,Fwas faced with symptoms that I could
OL,9,Fnot cope with I would like to have the
OL,10,Fautonomy to decide for myself that
OL,11,Fenough was enough and to do something
OL,12,Fabout it."
OL,14,FDumfries Pastor Mark Smith opposes the
OL,15,Fproposed legislation and wants to see
OL,16,Fbetter palliative care.
