OL,6,F"Had he been under even the inference
OL,7,Fof a pressure, he may well have taken
OL,8,Fthat decision and that would have been
OL,9,Fsuch a shame for me and my siblings,
OL,10,Fwe would have missed out on these
OL,11,Fprecious years with him in his later
OL,12,Flife."
