OL,6,FTwo doctors must be sure that you are
OL,7,Feligible and not being pressured or
OL,8,Fcoerced.
OL,10,FAfter they have agreed, there is a 14
OL,11,Fday reflection period, then you will
OL,12,Fbe given an approved substance that
OL,13,Fyou can choose to take yourself to end
OL,14,Fyour life.
OL,16,FAnalysis by Kieran Andrews, Political
OL,17,FEditor
OL,19,FThis is the third time that assisted
OL,20,Fdying legislation has been voted on at
OL,21,FHolyrood.
