OL,6,FThe division on Tuesday will be much,
OL,7,Fmuch closer than the previous attempts
OL,8,Fwhere there was no serious chance of
OL,9,Fthem advancing past their first
OL,10,Fparliamentary hurdle.
OL,12,FBut even if Liam McArthur's bill does
OL,13,Fmake it through, there is still a long
OL,14,Fway to go.
