OL,6,FWhatever the outcome, a bright spot
OL,7,Fhas come from the way the debate has
OL,8,Fbeen carried out.
OL,10,FMr McArthur is a well-respected MSP,
OL,11,Fwho has thought through his arguments
OL,12,Fand engaged positively with those he
OL,13,Fis trying to persuade and those who he
OL,14,Fcannot.
